  {
   "cell_type": "code",

   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# screening window \n",
    "# 0.1second window maximum amplitude \n",
    "#  maximum amplitude  0.1second window maximum amplitude       ! ->    \n",
    "#   \n",
    "#        ( ) -> main beat period.\n",
    "global_max = 0;\n",
    "max_times = [];\n",
    "Is_up = True;\n",
    "min_threshold = 0.05\n",
    "\n",
    "for i in range(int(len(y)/2205)):\n",
    "    temp_max = max(y[2205*i:2205*(i+1)])\n",
    "    if min_threshold < temp_max:\n",
    "        if global_max <= temp_max:\n",
    "            Is_up = True; \n",
    "            global_max = temp_max\n",
    "        elif Is_up != False :\n",
    "            Is_up = False;\n",
    "            global_max = temp_max\n",
    "            max_times.append(2205*i+np.argmax(y[2205*i:2205*(i+1)]))\n",
    "        else:\n",
    "            global_max = temp_max"
   ]
  },
